1)Income from continuing operations- Income Statement -Net Income from Continuing Operations and discontinued -(netIncomeFromContinuingOps)

2)  Total Accrual= Net profit - Net Cash from Operating Activities.

3) Net profit- https://www.google.com/search?q=calculate+net+profit&oq=calculate+net+profit&aqs=chrome.0.69i59l2j0l6.6108j0j4&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8

Income statement- Net Income Common Stockholders --> Net Income -(netIncome)

4) Net Cash from Operating Activities- Cash flow- Operating Cash Flow-->  Cash Flow from Continuing Operating Activities- (totalCashFromOperatingActivities)

5)Earnings= Income from Continuing Operations / Average Total Assets

6)Accrual component:Accruals/ Average Total Assets

7)Cashflow component= Income from Continuing Operations -Accruals / Average Total Assets 

